snippet.title: Anarchy Reigns - Official Trailer - TGS 2011 (PS3, Xbox 360)
snippet.description:
This video offers a sneak peek of the game's story mode as well as a great look at its characters and the many battles to come.

Read more here: http://www.gamespot.com/620290
